  "description": "<i>Buffy the Vampire Slayer: Sacrifice</i> is a survival horror game that takes place after season 7 of the television series. It's written by <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?developer=Rob+Deshotel\">Rob Deshotel</a>, one of the original writers of the television series. <br><br>In 24 levels the player explores locations from the show, including Sunnydale High and the Hellmouth. The player can opt to play in both first-or third-person perspective. In combat, the player can make use of martial arts, various weapons, and magic spells to defeat vampires and demons. <br><br>Spells are cast using stylus-based gestures. Hand to hand fighting sports a simple combo system similar to Fighting games. ",
